snippet.title: Schismo's Sideshow - Update 0.8.0
snippet.description:
You heard that right, update 0.8.0 is here! Included are new upgrades, a new paralysis effect, new art and more fantastic music by MicTV! 

Head on over to our Itch page to play the demo for Schismo's Sideshow, a topsy-turvy roguelite set inside of a bizarre carnival attraction!
